    Get events

    get_events.Rd

    Get schedule of events per season.

    Usage

    get_events(season_id, level = 0)

    Arguments

    season_id

    Character. Indicating the season by the last two digits of two following years, e.g. "1819" for 2018-2019.

    level

    Integer. Indicates the Cup level.

    • 0: All.

    • 1: World Cup.

    • 2: IBU Cup.

    • 3: Junior Cup.

    • 4: Other.

    Value

    A data.frame.

    Examples

    get_events("2223", "1")
